{"tid":1580412,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《願榮光歸香港》＠加拿大！","createTime":"2019-09-19T05:11:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T21:29:54.000Z","uid":324451,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"953781db50fa84318073c41c48e5596cac9a3045","tid":1580412,"uid":324451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T05:11:13.000Z","msg":"《願榮光歸香港》加拿大溫哥華列治文時代坊商場<br />\nGlory to Hong Kong - Aberdeen Centre, Richmond, BC, Canada<br />\n2019-09-14 14:00 PDT<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/s7gWRbYnPEs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fs7gWRbYnPEs&d=gqDWnnaI%2FM4dwC7GJUFj5Qpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=4b9ca480\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/s7gWRbYnPEs</a>"},{"pid":"86bee3463809c1b10dba37940faf0650438c13c8","tid":1580412,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T05:12:23.000Z","msg":"其實暫時用番呢支香港旗ok wor&quot;"},{"pid":"054cb728965a6e001795eb5346c6bc5b25dcaef1","tid":1580412,"uid":165246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T05:12:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">對家:</span></span><br />\n開始4點記者會，不斷帶風向引我地錯focus<br />\n二哥轉劉業成<br />\n林鄭主動分化示威者<br />\n黑社會越黎越多<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我地內部:</span></span><br />\n分化越黎越多<br />\n勇武開始捉左膠<br />\n左膠開始搞大台<br />\n現場既物資越黎越豐富 但引起既迴響越黎越細<br />\n每日出現大量對罵post、飛機post、恥笑popo記招post<br />\n<br />\n以為85罷工後局勢會改變，但反而好多14年失敗前出現過既先兆相繼浮現<br />\n講好左<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化，不割蓆，唔要大台，各有各做</span></span><br />\n希望唔淨係連登，而係出面既政黨、市民、和理非都要緊記呢幾個原則。<br />\n<br />\n而家每日資訊極多，希望大家撳入一個post討論前，諗諗大家拗黎係真係檢討、反思緊，定只係助長緊罵戰，後者的話可免則免。"},{"pid":"c80bfb6ed894ba30b2b860eaf8a7a410412325b1","tid":1580412,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T05:20:38.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n<br />\n針對中立淺藍黃嘅文宣【牆紙！】<br />\n第五期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1569904/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1569904/page/1</a><br />\n第四期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1547783/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1547783/page/1</a><br />\n第三期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1</a><br />\n第二期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1</a><br />\n第一期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1479130/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1479130/page/1</a><br />\nTG CHANNEL :<a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=gqDWnnaI%2FM4dwC7GJUFj5Qpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=18c233d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperENews</a>"},{"pid":"c9eb9a744a04c10e646e9aacf187474145be57e1","tid":1580412,"uid":288154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T09:56:43.000Z","msg":"《願榮光歸香港》香港電台 十大中文金曲 2019<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1582707\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1582707</a>"},{"pid":"25d0e8fa7d9b2fdbf10489dfc0c2d335b2eadb33","tid":1580412,"uid":55960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T08:22:06.000Z","msg":"係咪有個支那婆嘈？"},{"pid":"74d69fcace7fdc9623b0d746c391516e2d5db91b","tid":1580412,"uid":324451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25d0e8fa7d9b2fdbf10489dfc0c2d335b2eadb33","tid":1580412,"uid":55960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T08:22:06.000Z","msg":"係咪有個支那婆嘈？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T21:29:54.000Z","msg":"「返大陸！」＠加拿大<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592871\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592871</a>"}]}